tables.table_schema: liquidity_pools(id INT PRIMARY KEY, token1 VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, token2 VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, total_liquidity DECIMAL(18, 6) NOT NULL, created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL)

CREATE TABLE liquidity_pools (
    pool_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    token_a_id UUID,
    token_b_id UUID,
    pool_balance DECIMAL,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_swaps (
    swap_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    pool_id UUID,
    token_a_amount DECIMAL,
    token_b_amount DECIMAL,
    swap_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE tokens (
   token_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   token_name VARCHAR(255),
   token_symbol VARCHAR(10),
   token_balance DECIMAL,
   created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE swaps (
   swap_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   pool_id INT,
   token_in_id INT,
   token_out_id INT,
   amount_in DECIMAL,
   amount_out DECIMAL,
   created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE liquidity_pool (
    pool_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    token_1_id UUID NOT NULL,
    token_2_id UUID NOT NULL,
    reserves_1 DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    reserves_2 DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE swap (
    swap_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    pool_id UUID NOT NULL,
    token_in_id UUID NOT NULL,
    token_out_id UUID NOT NULL,
    amount_in DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    amount_out DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transaction (
    tx_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    pool_id UUID NOT NULL,
    action VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    amount DECIMAL NOT NULL
);
